ch.nolix.techAPI.resourceAPI

Interface IResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Named
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Resource

    public interface IResource
extends Named
    Of a IResource, a certain amount can be possessed. A IResource has a determined name. A IResource can have base resources. A IResource can serve as any of its base resources. A IResource is not mutable.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
